name: Tax Exemption
title: TE
definition:
Indicates that the customer has submitted a tax exemption
form to the provider.
validEntry:
Entry = Exempt From 
A = F & S 
B = F & C 
C = County or Local 
D = F & S & C 
E = F & S & M 
F = Federal 
G = F & S & C & M 
H = S & C 
I = S & M 
J = C & M 
K = F & M 
L = Letter on File 
M = Municipal 
N = Non Exempt 
P = S & C & M 
S = State/Province
usageNotes:
Required when the ACT field is “N” and the BAN
field is “N”, otherwise optional.
